1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在Suno主页中，有一个AI生成歌曲的排行榜，其中排名第一的是C-A-P-Y-B-A-R-A、第二首是Cyberpunk Starter，第三首是中文版的「水调歌头」。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="555" data-backw="562" data-height="1418" data-imgfileid="504976050" data-ratio="0.987037037037037" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1436" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb15vkIiaOXDekALZUeOc71rw7biaQm32cSmiczrgpXKJf2IgCqEic0DaGic1RicPgtqle7eflHkD5En2dqg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">接下来，听一下这首「水调歌头·明月几时有」，唱出了中国古典美。</span></p><p><mp-common-mpaudio class="js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=%E6%B0%B4%E8%B0%83%E6%AD%8C%E5%A4%B4&amp;play_length=1%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F" isaac2="1" low_size="219.39" source_size="219.4" high_size="847.73" name="水调歌头" play_length="112000" author="新智元" data-topic_id="" data-topic_name="" data-pluginname="insertaudio" data-trans_state="1" data-verify_state="3" voice_encode_fileid="MzI3MTA0MTk1MF8yNjUyNDU5NzU2"></mp-common-mpaudio></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">还有这首现代感的音乐「著了魔」，听完真的有种恋爱的赶脚。</span></p><p><mp-common-mpaudio class="js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=%E8%91%97%E4%BA%86%E9%AD%94&amp;play_length=3%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F" isaac2="1" low_size="369.23" source_size="369.2" high_size="1411.54" name="著了魔" play_length="181000" author="新智元" data-topic_id="" data-topic_name="" data-pluginname="insertaudio" data-trans_state="1" data-verify_state="3" voice_encode_fileid="MzI3MTA0MTk1MF8yNjUyNDU5NzU1"></mp-common-mpaudio></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8